high_descs: Move to the toilet on your right.
Pick up the sponge on the toilet.
Bring the sponge to the sink behind you.
Wash the sponge in sink with water.
Bring the cleaned sponge back to the toilet in the opposite corner from the sink.
Put the cleaned sponge on the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned sponge on the toilet.

high_descs: turn right, go to the toilet to the right
pick up green sponge from toilet
place green sponge in sink, turn on water, turn off water, pick up clean green sponge from sink
turn around, go to the toilet to the left
place green sponge on right side of toilet tank
anns.task_desc: place clean green sponge on toilet tank

high_descs: pick up the sponge from the back of the toilet
take the sponge to the sink
put the sponge in the sink, wash, then remove
take the sponge back to the toilet
put the sponge on the right side of the toilet tank
anns.task_desc: wash the sink with the sponge and put it back
